---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import quotes from '../data/quotes.json';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---
<BaseLayout title="李卓衡 | 个人网站" description="Zhuoheng Li - MS in Management & Analytics @ NYU | Data Analytics & Data Engineering">
  <section class="hero-welcome">
    <h2 class="welcome-text content-zh" data-i18n="heroWelcomeZh">欢迎来到我的小站</h2>
    <h2 class="welcome-text content-en" data-i18n="heroWelcomeEn">Welcome</h2>
    <p class="quote-line" id="random-quote" aria-live="polite">
      <span class="content-zh" id="quote-zh"></span>
      <span class="content-en" id="quote-en"></span>
    </p>
  </section>
  <script define:vars={{ quotes }}>
    (function () {
      var q = quotes[Math.floor(Math.random() * quotes.length)];
      var zh = document.getElementById('quote-zh');
      var en = document.getElementById('quote-en');
      if (zh) zh.textContent = '"' + q.zh + '" — ' + q.authorZh;
      if (en) en.textContent = '"' + q.en + '" — ' + q.authorEn;
    })();
  </script>
  <section id="about" class="home-about">
    <h2 class="section-title" data-i18n="sectionAbout">关于我</h2>
    <div class="about-content">
      <div class="content-zh">
        <p>目前就读于<strong>纽约大学（NYU）管理与分析（Management & Analytics）</strong>硕士项目，研究方向偏向技术型数据分析与数据工程。</p>
        <p>我的本科专业为<strong>音乐表演（古琴）</strong>，在系统学习数据分析与编程之前，我长期接受的是艺术与演奏训练。这段跨学科背景让我在面对复杂问题时，既具备结构化分析能力，也保持对细节和整体逻辑的高度敏感。</p>
        <p>在研究生阶段，我系统学习并实践了 <strong>Python、SQL、关系型数据库与数据处理流程</strong>，熟悉从数据采集、清洗、建模分析到可视化呈现的完整数据分析工作流。我曾参与多个数据分析与数据建模项目，包括广告与用户行为分析、用户分群与 RFM 用户价值模型构建、运营指标体系设计以及多源数据整合分析，能够将业务问题转化为可落地的数据分析方案。</p>
        <p>我目前专注于<strong>数据分析与数据工程</strong>方向，希望未来从事以数据驱动业务决策、数据建模、数据平台建设，以及支持 AI 与智能应用的数据分析与数据工程相关岗位。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content-en">
        <p>I am currently pursuing a Master's degree in <strong>Management & Analytics at New York University (NYU)</strong>, with a focus on technical data analytics and data engineering.</p>
        <p>My undergraduate major was <strong>Music Performance (Guqin)</strong>. Before systematically studying data analytics and programming, I spent years training in art and performance. This interdisciplinary background enables me to approach complex problems with both structured analytical thinking and a keen sensitivity to details and overall logic.</p>
        <p>During my graduate studies, I have systematically learned and practiced <strong>Python, SQL, relational databases, and data processing workflows</strong>, and I am familiar with the complete data analytics workflow from data collection, cleaning, modeling, to visualization. I have participated in multiple data analytics and modeling projects, including advertising and user behavior analysis, user segmentation and RFM value modeling, operational metrics system design, and multi-source data integration analysis, with the ability to translate business problems into actionable data analytics solutions.</p>
        <p>I am currently focused on <strong>data analytics and data engineering</strong>, and I hope to pursue roles in data-driven business decision-making, data modeling, data platform development, and data analytics/engineering positions that support AI and intelligent applications.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .home-about { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }
  .home-about .about-content p {
    margin: 0 0 0.85rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .home-about .about-content p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .hero-welcome {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1.5rem 0 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .welcome-text {
    font-family: "Dancing Script", "ZCOOL XiaoWei", "Noto Serif SC", cursive;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 8vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
  .quote-line {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-style: italic;
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 540px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    line-height: 1.5;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
  }
  .hero-welcome {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
  }
</style>
